<div class="ss-prose">
  <p>shortstory.ink is designed to feel like a private members’ literary workshop: calm, spacious, and typography-led.</p>
  <p>It supports adult writers who want structure, feedback, and continuity — without noise, gamification, or generic edtech patterns.</p>
  <h2>What it optimises for</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Precise inline feedback that stays with the text.</li>
    <li>A writer’s commonplace system for saving craft moves and passages.</li>
    <li>Reading that’s genuinely pleasant to stay with.</li>
  </ul>
</div>
